@startuml
title Siemens U273 Plugin - Package Dependencies

skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "u273_core" as core {
  [types]
  [units]
  [math]
  [parameter ranges]
  [tables]
}

package "u273_dsp" as dsp {
  [U273DspEngine]
  [DetectorEnvelope]
  [B6BridgeRealtimeModel]
  [GainReductionComputer]
}

package "u273_reference" as ref {
  [ScientificReferenceModel]
  [ReferenceValidator]
  [GoldenReader]
}

package "u273_plugin" as plugin {
  [PluginProcessor]
  [PluginEditor]
  [ParameterBridge]
  [PresetManager]
  [MeterBridge]
}

package "u273_assets" as assets {
  [presets]
  [golden files]
  [calibration tables]
}

package "u273_tests" as tests {
  [unit tests]
  [regression tests]
  [benchmarks]
}

dsp --> core
ref --> core
ref --> assets
plugin --> core
plugin --> dsp
plugin --> assets
tests ..> core
tests ..> dsp
tests ..> ref
tests ..> plugin
tests ..> assets

note right of core
No dependency on JUCE UI.
No dependency on plugin wrapper.
Stable, small, reusable.
end note

note right of dsp
Realtime package.
Must stay independent from:
- PluginEditor
- APVTS details
- files
- logs
- reference MNA
end note

note bottom
Package rule: dependencies must remain acyclic.
The plugin wraps DSP; DSP never calls the plugin.
end note

@enduml

